--- SCENARIO: /lobbyInfo drops an anchor that backlinks to the live status message ---
# The status message already carries everything, so /lobbyInfo no longer re-prints lobby state — it
# posts a short anchor that replies to (backlinks) the status message so players can jump to it. With
# no lobby it just says so.

--- CHAT ---
alice: /lobbyInfo
ambotorix: No active lobby*       # nothing to anchor to yet

alice: /lobby
bob: /register
ambotorix: <status *Players (2): alice, bob*>

bob: /lobbyInfo
ambotorix: 📌 Lobby status* <backlink>
ambotorix:                        # only the "no lobby" reply and the anchor were ever posted
